Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Bicentennial year
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z98h9
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 4 Jan 1976
Bicentennial year in the land of unbounded commercial opportunity. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.